The '''1981 Pittsburgh Panthers football team''' represented the [[University of Pittsburgh]] in the 1981 college football season. Despite having one loss, the Panthers were selected as National Champions by the National Championship Foundation and Montgomery Full Season Championship,<ref>[http://www.cfbdatawarehouse.com/data/div_ia/bigeast/pittsburgh/all_national_champs.php College Football Data Warehouse; Pittsburgh All National Championships, accessdate=2009-01-29]</ref> although a national championship is not claimed by the school for this year nor are they are not popularly recognized that season's national champions.
